{"tid":470781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州地鐵推Apple Pay支付入閘　最平2毫乘車","createTime":"2017-11-16T15:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T10:34:11.000Z","uid":2314,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7a1cf904152083d8daad47a3fe277c0cedd525","tid":470781,"uid":2314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/232907_18ed205374bb9f94b16f3307d6591334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F232907_18ed205374bb9f94b16f3307d6591334.jpg&h=698f0152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地電子支付已成大勢所趨，廣州地鐵表示，目前全線網絡支持通過Apple Pay使用銀聯手機「閃付」過閘，從周二（26日）起至今年底以該种方式乘坐地鐵，每程更能夠享受立減1.8元（人民幣．下同）的優惠，以最低票價2元計算，即是0.2元便可坐地鐵。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，目前廣州地鐵已有逾6000部入閘機配備了此項功能，乘客可用安裝了iOS 11的iPhone或安裝了WatchOS 4的Apple Watch上加入銀聯卡，便可以享受每日兩程，每次減1.8元的優惠，這比使用廣州地鐵羊城通卡，每月使用16次後可享6折優惠更加實惠。 <br />\n<br />\n內地網民紛紛對此表示支持，「方便又實惠，又可以少帶一張卡了」、「現在可以放心只帶鑰匙和手機出門了」、「如果巴士也可以這樣就好了」；但亦有人笑指「難道是歧視Android用戶嗎？不開心沒得閃付！」、「借此機會可以看看誰先用上IPhone X」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170927/mobile/bkncn-20170927141936742-0927_05011_001.html?eventPath=cn_news&amp;eventID=402882b0596c9cfb015986b816483787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170927%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20170927141936742-0927_05011_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dcn_news%26eventID%3D402882b0596c9cfb015986b816483787&d=ndziCs%2BJvTtf4JlSxQWcGv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=3fd222e3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170927/mobile/bkncn-20170927141936742-0927_05011_001.html?eventPath=cn_news&amp;eventID=402882b0596c9cfb015986b816483787</a>"},{"pid":"dbb5eebf00e91bfadb249f881002bc32e7d72dc9","tid":470781,"uid":80072,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解唔掃br code<img src=\"/assets/faces/no